tion.\n        <\/p>\n      <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\"luna-features-grid\">\n        \n        <div class=\"luna-feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"luna-icon-circle\">\n            <svg class=\"luna-icon-svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n              <path d=\"M20.24 12.24a6 6 0 0 0-8.49-8.49L5 10.5V19h8.5z\"><\/path>\n              <line x1=\"16\" y1=\"8\" x2=\"2\" y2=\"22\"><\/line>\n              <line x1=\"17.5\" y1=\"15\" x2=\"9\" y2=\"15\"><\/line>\n            <\/svg>\n          <\/div>\n          <span class=\"luna-feature-title\">Calms Racing Thoughts<\/span>\n          <p class=\"luna-feature-desc\">\n            <strong>Ultra-fine glass beads distribute gentle pressure evenly<\/strong> around your eye sockets—activating your parasympathetic nervous system and telling your brain \"it's safe to rest now.\" Like a weighted blanket, but just for your eyes.\n          <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"luna-feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"luna-icon-circle\">\n            <svg class=\"luna-icon-svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n              <path d=\"M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z\"><\/path>\n            <\/svg>\n          <\/div>\n          <span class=\"luna-feature-title\">Protects Melatonin<\/span>\n          <p class=\"luna-feature-desc\">\n            <strong>Zero light leaks<\/strong> means your brain produces uninterrupted melatonin—the hormone that makes you sleepy. Even a sliver of light from streetlamps disrupts this. Luna Nord blocks it all.\n          <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div class=\"luna-feature-item\">\n          <div class=\"luna-icon-circle\">\n            <svg class=\"luna-icon-svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\">\n              <path d